title: Oceansize Discography 2001-2010 MP3 320 kbps CBR
description:
----- Oceansize Discography 2001-2010 MP3 320 kbps CBR ---------------

This is a collection of all LPs, EPs and singles produced by Oceansize from 2001-2010. The torrent contains only the .mp3 files, with album artwork embedded.

As stated, all files have a constant bit rate of 320 kbps. Albums have been normalized at 89.0 db gain.

----- Contents -------------------------------------------------------

LPs:

2003 - Effloresce
2005 - Everyone Into Position
2007 - Frames
2010 - Self Preserved While The Bodies Float Up

EPs:

2001 - A Very Still Movement
2002 - Relapse
2004 - Music For Nurses
2009 - Home & Minor

Singles:

2003 - One Day All This Could Be Yours
2003 - Remember Where You Are
2004 - Catalyst
2005 - Heaven Alive
2006 - New Pin
2010 - SuperImposer

----- Omissions ------------------------------------------------------

The Amputee EP and Saturday Morning Breakfast Show single, both released in 1999, are not included. These records were released while Oceansize was unsigned and are very hard to track down.

The live Frames DVD is not included, nor is the Feed to Feed box-set, though I may upload the latter eventually.

----------------------------------------------------------------------

If you like their music, please support Oceansize by buying the albums!
